name: LuckyNumber
0:
”Alexa, ask Lucky Number what is my lucky number”
”Alexa, tell Lucky Number to tell me my lucky number”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: lucky number
des: Lucky Number chooses your lucky number for you whenever you need it. Use it for guidance, lottery numbers, and all of life's major decisions. You can ask it for a lucky number as many times as you need to and it will always give you an answer.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
